name: Travel Suit Slim Fit Striped Wool Blazer
description: Striped suit blazer in comfort wool, made with the utmost care by the true master tailors of our seasoned brand. Our Travel Suit selection is made from exceptionally wearable fabric that follows and adapts to the movements of the body, ensuring complete comfort. They are designed for a modern man who is always on the move between work meetings and informal gatherings. These garments guarantee maximum comfort and impeccable style at all times. The Italian fabrics used stand out for their excellent technical qualities and the high twist technology of their threads, providing great resistance to creasing and fast recovery. At the same time, these fabrics have a natural stretch, allowing great freedom of movement and comfort. The suits also have a water repellent finish which is ideal for rainy climates. Featuring a slim fit, notched lapel collar with buttonhole, custom undercollar, two-button fastening, two side flap pockets, one besom pocket at the chest, long sleeves with four-button cuffs, two back vents, lining and several inside pockets. The back length for size 50 is 74 cm. Made in Egypt.

Made in Portugal.

name: Kashbah Sunset Eau de Parfum
description: The desert is always an ideal place for magic to occur. And from that inhospitable and mysterious environment comes Kashbah Sunset, a formula whose warm top notes hatch and intoxicate with the same vigour of a warm and dusty dawn in a southern land. This is a perfume that belongs to the oriental - woody family. It is addictive, with exotic notes, yet it is also very well balanced, transporting those desert aromas. The main ingredients are vetiver, cedar and saffron. Harry Fremont, creator of the fragrance, is the only perfumer to have won The French Society of Perfumers’ prize for two consecutive years. He believes that an excellent perfume should have its own recognisable character, signature and aura. The materials used to hold the perfume reinforce the quality and exclusivity of this collection. The bottle has elegant lines and the top, made of resin, is the most characteristic part. In the case of Kashbah Sunset, it has a brown tone. In addition, the perfume comes with a pouch to help protect it.

name: Sandy Papyrus Perfume and Candle Pack

name: Stainless Steel Lithium Ion Gold Trimmer - Limited Edition
description: Heavy duty, stainless steel blades and body, the Wahl Lithium Ion Trimmer gives you everything you need to take care of all your grooming needs. You get a 4 hour run time, 2 times the torque compared to Wahl's standard trimmer. The world wide voltage makes this trimmer the best travel tool you will ever own.

name: Sonicare Diamond Clean Rose Gold Electric Toothbrush
description: Achieve whiter, healthier teeth from the most elegant Philips Sonicare ever. The Philips Diamond Clean electric toothbrush removes up to 7 times more plaque than a manual toothbrush. Includes dual charging system (charger glass and USB travel case), allowing you to take your Diamond Clean anywhere and everywhere.

name: Series 9000 Wet & Dry Prestige Electric Shaver
description: The Philips S9000 Prestige glides smoothly over your skin, while cutting each hair exceptionally close - even on a 7-day beard. The result is smoothness that touches you, and closeness you can feel.

name: Wahl Rechargeable Beard Trimmer & Accessories Gift Set
description: Cordless rechargeable trimmer, set includes 4 blades, beard oil and brush, features barber comb, comes in branded case.

name: Beard Duo set
description: Two piece beard grooming set, original beard shampoo and conditioner, two-in-one shampoo and conditioner, contains aloe vera, camelina oil and green tea, designed to nourish your beard leaving it soft and fresh, original beard balm, contains aloe vera, camelina oil and green tea, conditions and moisturises your beard, free from artificial colours and synthetic fragrances, use after shampoo and conditioner for best results, vegan-friendly products.

name: Men Expert Hydra Sensitive Moisturiser50ml
description: Targets dry, uncomfortable skin, instantly soothes and hydrates, suitable for sensitive skin.

name: Souffle Marais Perfume and Candle Pack
description: Two bottles of Souffle Marais perfume (100 ml and 10 ml) and a scented candle.

name: Pack of 3 Eau de Parfum
description: Pack of three perfumes (Souffle Marais, Manhattan Light and Evening Whispers). Each bottle is 30 ml with a top fitting the described essence.

name: Manhattan Light Eau de Parfum
description: Manhattan Light is a modern perfume which embodies and reflects the concept of elegance that has turned the most cosmopolitan city in the world into a contemporary fashion icon. It belongs to the floral - fruity fragrance family and its freshness and lightness are appreciated in its top notes, with its main ingredients being peony, bergamot and musk. The fragrance’s perfumer Olivier Cresp was named Master Perfumer in 2006 and Perfumer of the Year in 2007. He is a lover of all things sophisticated and therefore his perfumery is always carefully crafted, delicately prepared and is timeless. The materials used to hold the perfume reinforce the quality and exclusivity of this collection. The bottle has elegant lines and the top, made of resin, is the most characteristic part. In the case of Manhattan Light, it has a marbled tone. In addition, the perfume comes with a pouch to help protect it.

name: Evening Whispers Perfume and Candle Pack
description: Two bottles of Evening Whispers perfume (100 ml and 10 ml) and a scented candle.

name: Evening Whispers Eau de Parfum
description: Evening Whispers is a cocooning, intense and mysterious fragrance with an exceptional combination of charismatic and unmistakeable fruity, floral and spicy notes that leave a vibrant, instantly noticed trail. It belongs to the chypre - fruity fragrance family and is distinguishable for the sweetness of its notes, with its main ingredients being rose, praline and red berries. The fragrance’s perfumer, Amadine Clerc Marie loves to look for an idea, draft a plan and then see how everything fits together. She is a very visual person and always creates images of the things she wishes to make. The materials used to hold the perfume reinforce the quality and exclusivity of this collection. The bottle has elegant lines and the top, made of resin, is the most characteristic part. In the case of Evening Whispers, it has a crimson tone. In addition, the perfume comes with a pouch to help protect it.

name: Holidaze Face Palette
description: For multiple looks, contains nine shades, three matte contour, bronze and highlight shades, six spotlight highlighters (including two mega-sparkle shades).

name: Deep Sleep Pillow Talk
description: Set of two products, designed to help you sleep, oil enriched with Lavender, uses the therapeutic qualities of Lavender to relieve tension and insomnia.

name: Grand Illusion Liquid Lip - Rave Bunny
description: Too glam to give a damn, ultra-holographic iridescent pearl finish, creates the illusion of plumped lips, cooling sensation makes lips feel fuller, glides on smoothly - wears evenly.

name: i-Light Pro IPL6500AU IPL Long Term Hair Removal System
description: If you’re looking for beautifully smooth skin, then your hair removal saviour is here – the Remington i-LIGHT PRO+ Face & Body is fast, effective and gentle on the skin. Dermatologist endorsed and Choice recommended, this hair removal system can achieve salon standard results in the comfort and convenience of your own home. Designed for use on both the body and face, this technologically advanced device harnesses innovative Intense Pulsed Light (IPL) technology to achieve up to 94% fewer hairs after just 3 treatments!

name: Supersonic Hair Dryer - Iron and Fuchsia
description: Discover what Dyson engineering can do for your hair. The Dyson Supersonic™ hair dryer is engineered is engineered for balance and designed for fast drying and precision styling at the same time. With intelligent heat control for shine, magnetic attachments and powered by the Dyson digital motor V9, the Dyson Supersonic is the hair dryer re-thought.

name: 3 Stripe T-shirt
description: Regular fit, 100% cotton.

name: Tech 1/2 Zip Top
description: Giving optimal coverage, this ½ zip hooded top from Under Armour is made for explosive gym sessions. Built from a UA tech fabric, the Moisture Transport System removes sweat from the body, whilst the loose fit can be layered all year round.

name: Rival Fleece Joggers
description: Comfort is key with the Rival joggers from Under Armour – a lightweight, ultra-soft option for downtime days. With a stretchy elasticated waist, ribbed cuffs and a tapered leg, the classic Under Armour embroidery at the leg delivers a signature feel.

name: Unstoppable Move Light Full Zip Hoodie - Light Grey Heather
description: This Under Armour Move Light full zip hoodie is built using Charged Cotton®, which has all the regular comfort as standard but dries faster. The four-way stretch construction moves better in every direction, with darting at the shoulders and elbows providing a more tailored fit.

name: Chuck Taylor All Star Hi-Tops
description: Chuck Taylor trainers are chic, stylish and simple - the perfect versatile shoe for any adventure. Chuck Taylor hi top plimsolls boast a strong canvas upper which bears the original Chuck Taylor patch logo to the inside. Two perforated holes help to circulate air inside the shoe. These Chuck Taylor Converse plimsolls are available in a range of funky colours including white, red, navy and black.

name: Air Max 95
description: Inspiration for the Air Max 95 came from the human anatomy. It imitates the spine in all-black and features a breathable mesh upper that’s injected with scattered air-sole units. Nike branding is included with a woven tab to the tongue, embossed Air Max branding to the heel and the understated swoosh to the rear. A full length midsole presents luxe cushioning on impact.

name: Game Time Tracksuit - Medium Grey Heather
description: Stay warm with the Game Time tracksuit from adidas. Made using recycled French terry, the full zip track top features colour-block style and includes an adjustable hood for coverage. The matching pants are cut with a tapered fit with an elasticated waistband for comfort.

name: Basic Jog Pants
description: Get the athleisure look with this basic jog pant from V by Very. Rendered in 100% cotton, this is the perfect pick for post-workout wear, or for just daily leisurewear. An elasticated drawstring waist gives a personal fit around the midriff.

name: Football Tracksuit
description: The best of the beautiful game mixed with sleek, ergonomic lines, this Puma tracksuit comes with cool colour contrasting and a slim, tailored fit. The jacket has a full zip closure alongside forwarded shoulder seams that allow for total freedom of movement.

name: Polo Ralph Lauren Golf Perform Pique Polo
description: An American style icon since 1972, this polo shirt by Ralph Lauren Golf is meticulously made with a hint of stretch in the fabric. On a sleek black backdrop, the button construction is complete with the signature embroidered pony at the chest.

name: Sportswear Gym Vintage Full Zip Hoodie
description: A Gym Vintage hoodie by Nike Sportswear fuses complete comfort and throwback vibes to deliver an essential addition in your capsule collection. Lightweight and soft to the touch, it's the perfect partner to your athleisure looks.

name: Sportswear Woven Jacket - Wheat
description: Whether you're covering up for your commute to the gym, or kicking back on rest days - this woven jacket by Nike Sportswear will fast become your new season staple. Dri-FIT technology is partnered with mesh to keep you dry, light and comfortable whatever your day brings!

name: Trefoil Tee
description: Elevate your basics to iconic status with adidas Originals and their Trefoil T-shirt. In a navy blue hue, it's soft to the touch for complete comfort, while the oversized logo to the front rounds off the look.

name: Old Skool Trainers
description: In black with a tonal outsole they’re infused with a vintage aesthetic that’s never in danger of going out of style. The mid silhouette is an iconic shape, whilst the tonal stripe branding to the side is a familiar touch. Completed with the ‘Off The Wall’ logo to the heel, it’s the dream of retro sneaker heads.

name: Lace Up Trainer
description: Step into old school style courtesy of River Island and the iconic Superstar. Presented in white and gold, they're a fresh spin on a heritage classic that boast the same comfortable cupsole and padded collar as the original pair, and the shell toe cap solidifies their place in the sneaker halls of fame.

name: Run Essential Jacket
description: Rack up the miles whatever the weather with this jacket by Nike Running. The hood, zip front and water repellent finish are ideal for wet weather and keep you covered until you've crossed the finish line, while reflectivity allows you to sprint in safety.

name: Sportswear JDI Tee
description: Bring the look and feel of your gym gear to your capsule collection with the Nike Sportswear JDI tee. In red, it's a bold pick that's elevated to iconic status with Nike's signature call to action sitting front and centre.

name: Training Power Legging
description: Made for intense gym sessions - the Power leggings by Nike Training work to support your muscles during every rep and reduce vibration so you can use more of your energy on the workout in hand!

name: Sportswear Woven Jacket
description: Perfect for commutes to and from the gym or kicking back on rest days - a woven jacket by Nike Sportswear puts a sporty spin on your cover up collection. Lined with mesh, it features a large hood and zip fastening to allow you to control the cooling and coverage.

name: D2M High Rise 3 Stripe Tight
description: These high rise leggings by adidas are designed for gym sessions when you need to move freely and fully without any distractions. The high rise and wide waistband creates a sleek fit and feel with plenty of coverage, while quick-drying fabric keeps you focused on every rep.
